					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The trick to fast matrix multiplies is knowing what's in your matrices, and thus where all the zeroes are.
<br />
<br />If you think the basic transforms are bad, you should see all the stuff that goes on after you get the thing projected. Perspective-correct interpolation is a lovely mess.</div>

